TER.TERdecoder
Class Decoder

java.lang.Object
  TER.TERdecoder.Decoder

public class Decoder
extends java.lang.Object

Main class of TER decoder application. It receives all parameters, checks its validity and runs TER decoder. Usage example:
  construct
  setParameters
  run

Version:
1.2
Author:

CVerbose

boolean[] CVerbose
Show some information about decoding process. Each value is boolean (false means NO show, true means show).

Each value represents the following:

  • 0- Information about time and used memory for each compression stage
  • 1- TER parameters
  • 1- TER decoder messages
